snippet.textDisplay: I’m a fan of Fantano. I enjoy his criticisms and I do trust his reviews for the most part. However, I feel that music rings different for people who are in different places in life and because of this, Anthony often misses the connection to certain music. I was disheartened to see how little Fantano enjoyed Macs album Swimming and how harshly he received it because that album to me was near perfect (perfecto 👌 if you will). I was going through a difficult time in life when Swimming was released and I can’t begin to explain how much I needed to hear that album when it came out. That album was a 10/10 for me. I hope one day Fantano can revisit that album, perhaps when he’s in a different emotional state and hear that album for what it was meant to be.
